translation: Mag-iipon ka ng %s minecoin gamit ang iyong subscription sa Marketplace Pass!

source_string: Unable to connect to the world. Please check your connection to the internet and try again.
translation: Hindi makakonekta sa mundo. Pakitingnan uli ang koneksiyon mo sa internet at subukang muli.

source_string: Appearance is taking a long time to load. Proceeding with world generation...
translation: Masyado nang matagal naglo-load ang appearance. Tumutuloy sa henerasyon ng mundo...

source_string: This may take a few minutes.
translation: Maaari itong magtagal ng ilang minuto.

source_string: Please do not exit the game. Exiting might corrupt the export.
translation: Huwag umalis sa laro. Maaaring i-corrupt ng pag-alis ang export.

source_string: This may take a few moments
translation: Maaari itong magtagal ng ilang sandali

source_string: This may take a few moments...
translation: Maaari itong magtagal ng ilang sandali...

source_string: This may take a few moments
translation: Maaari itong magtagal ng ilang sandali
Ina-upload ang mga file ng mundo...

source_string: World upload failed. Would you like to try again?
translation: Nabigong mag-upload ang mundo. Gusto mo bang subukang muli?
Isine-save ang Resource Pack ng Mundo

source_string: Invalid world file. Please reopen your world, save, then try again.
translation: Imbalido ang file ng mundo. Pakibukas uli ang mundo, i-save, at subukan uli.

source_string: Your game is being saved. Please do not turn off your device.
translation: Isine-save ang laro mo. Huwag patayin ang device mo.

source_string: This may take a few moments
translation: Maaari itong magtagal ng ilang sandali

source_string: We couldn't confirm if your world uploaded properly. Please join your Realm to check, then try again if it hasn't been updated to the new world.
translation: Hindi namin makumpirma kung maayos na nai-upload ang mundo mo. Salihan ang Realm mo para tingnan, at subukang muli kung hindi pa siya nai-update sa bagong mundo.

source_string: Failed to find a place to upload your world. Maybe check your internet connection?
translation: Walang mahanap na lugar na mapapag-uploadan ng iyong mundo. Siguro tingnan mo ang koneksiyon mo sa internet?

source_string: It looks like you do not own the Marketplace template this world is based on. You can purchase it from Minecraft Marketplace.
translation: Mukhang hindi mo pagmamay-ari ang template sa Marketplace na pinagbasehan nitong mundo. Mabibili mo ito sa Minecraft Marketplace.

source_string: We couldn't pack your world file for upload. Maybe your hard drive is full?
translation: Hindi namin ma-pack ang iyong file ng mundo para i-upload. Siguro puno ang hard drive mo?

source_string: Something went wrong while preparing to upload your world. If this keeps happening, restarting your device may help.
translation: Nagkaproblema sa paghanda ng pag-upload ng mundo mo. Kung tuloy itong mangyayari, maaaring makatulong ang pag-restart ng device mo.

source_string: This world can't be opened because of a directory issue in the pack.
translation: Hindi mabuksan itong mundo dahil sa problema sa directory sa pack.

source_string: You do not own one or more of the applied packs
translation: Hindi mo pagmamay-ari ang isa o marami pang nakalagay na pack
Tapos nang i-load ang mga Splitscreen Appearance.

source_string: The world name contains words that others may find offensive and cannot be used.
translation: May lamang masamang salita ang pangalan ng mundo na maaaring makasira at hindi ito magagamit.

source_string: You're playing in a world with Add-Ons! This will add new features to your Minecraft world.
translation: Naglalaro ka sa mundong may Add-On! Magdadagdag ito ng bagong mga feature sa iyong mundo sa Minecraft.

source_string: Don't stop with just one! You can load multiple Add-Ons onto a single world at once.
translation: Huwag malagay sa iisa! Makapaglo-load ka ng maraming Add-On nang sabay-sabay sa isang mundo.

source_string: Advanced Tip: A Resource Pack can change the textures of different blocks and entities.
translation: Advanced Tip: Mababago ng Resource Pack ang texture ng iba-ibang bloke at entidad.

source_string: Advanced Tip: A Behavior Pack can change how different items, entities, or blocks work.
translation: Advanced Tip: Mababago ng Behavior Pack ang paraan kung paano gumagana ang iba-ibang aytem, entidad, at bloke.

source_string: Advanced Tip: An Add-On includes both a Behavior Pack and a Resource Pack. Make sure both packs are activated to ensure the Add-On works!
translation: Advanced Tip: Ang Add-On ay may parehas na Behavior Pack at Resource Pack. Tiyaking aktibado ang parehas sa kanila para siguraduhing gumagana ang Add-On!

source_string: Add-Ons add new blocks, items, or mobs to your worlds.
translation: Nagdadagdag ang Add-On ng bagong bloke, aytem, o mob sa mundo mo.

source_string: Worlds and Add-ons are complex! While some work great together, you might get funky results with others.
translation: Komplikado ang Mundo at Add-on! Kahiman may ilang gumagana nang magkasama, maaari kang makakita sa iba ng kakaibang mga resulta.

source_string: More Add-Ons mean more fun, but the game might take longer to load.
translation: Sa dami ng Add-On mas sasaya ang laro, pero maaaring mas tatagal mag-load ang laro.
Nabigong I-sync ang Data ng Mundo
Tagumpay na Nai-sync ang Data ng Mundo

source_string: Some optional resource packs applied to this world include ray tracing. Your device is not compatible with advanced lighting and texture features so you will see the world without these advanced effects.
translation: May opsiyonal na resource pack na nakalagay sa mundong ito na may ray tracing. Hindi compatible ang device mo sa advanced na pagliliwanag at feature sa texture kaya makikita mo ang mundo nang wala nitong mga advanced na effect.

source_string: Some optional and required resource packs applied to this world include ray tracing. Your device is not compatible with advanced lighting and texture features so you will see the world without these advanced effects.
translation: May opsiyonal at kailangang resource pack na nakalagay sa mundong ito na may ray tracing. Hindi compatible ang device mo sa advanced na pagliliwanag at feature sa texture kaya makikita mo ang mundo nang wala nitong mga advanced na effect.

source_string: Some required resource packs applied to this world include ray tracing. Your device is not compatible with advanced lighting and texture features so you will see the world without these advanced effects.
translation: May kailangang resource pack na nakalagay sa mundong ito na may ray tracing. Hindi compatible ang device mo sa advanced na pagliliwanag at feature sa texture kaya makikita mo ang mundo nang wala nitong mga advanced na effect.

source_string: This world has optional Resource Packs applied to it. Would you like to download them before you join?
translation: May opsiyonal na Resource Pack na nakalagay sa mundong ito. Gusto mo ba itong i-download bago sumali?

source_string: This world has optional Resource Packs and required Resource Packs from Add-Ons applied to it. Would you like to download all packs or only the ones required to join?
translation: May opsiyonal na Resource Pack at kailangang Resource Pack galing sa Add-On na nakalagay. Gusto mo bang i-download ang lahat ng pack o ang kailangan na lang para sumali?

source_string: This world has required Resource Packs from Add-Ons applied to it. Would you like to download them and join?
translation: May kailangang na Resource Pack galing sa Add-On na nakalagay sa mundong ito. Gusto mo ba itong i-download at sumali?

source_string: The owner of this world requires players to download all Resource Packs applied to it. Would you like to download them and join?
translation: Inuutos ng may-ari ng mundong ito na i-download ang lahat ng nakalagay na Resource Pack. Gusto mo ba silang i-download at sumali?

source_string: Could not sync your world data. Would you like to try again?
translation: Hindi mai-sync ang data ng mundo. Gusto mo ba subukang muli?

source_string: The world is not fully synced or has been corrupted. Try playing the world on a console where it's in a good state and try migrating it again.
translation: Hindi buong nai-sync o na-corrupt ang mundong ito. Subukang laruin ang mundo sa console na maayos ang estado at subukang ilipat uli.

source_string: Local save successful but cloud sync failed due to quota. Free cloud space by deleting worlds from the settings menu.
translation: Tagumpay ang lokal na pag-save pero nabigo ang cloud sync dahil sa quota. Magbigay ng lugar sa cloud gamit ang pagbura ng mundo sa menu ng settings.

source_string: Not enough local free space to support cloud sync.
translation: Kulang ang libreng lokal na space para suportahan ang cloud sync.

source_string: The world has been corrupted. Please report this at bugs.mojang.com
translation: Na-corrupt ang mundo. Iulat ito sa bugs.mojang.com

source_string: Syncing this world is taking a long time. Would you like to continue waiting?
translation: Masyadong matagal ang pag-sync ng mundong ito. Gusto mo bang magpatuloy maghintay?

source_string: This project has Resource Packs applied to it. Would you like to download them before you join?
translation: May nakalagay na Resource Pack sa proyektong ito. Gusto mo ba itong i-download bago sumali?

source_string: This project has Resource Packs applied to it that you must download to join. Would you like to download them and join?
translation: May Resource Pack na nakalagay sa proyektong ito na kailangan mong i-download para sumali. Gusto mo ba silang i-download at sumali?

source_string: Converting project to world and making a copy of your project...
translation: Ginagawang mundo ang proyekto at gumagawa ng kopya ng proyekto mo...

source_string: You are not currently connected to wifi. Mobile data charges might apply.
translation: Hindi kasalukuyang nakakonekta sa wifi. Maaaring ipairal ang gastos sa Mobile data.

source_string: The quiz will open in a new window. You may return to Minecraft after you have completed the quiz.
translation: Bubukas ang quiz sa bagong window. Makababalik ka sa Minecraft pagkatapos mo gawin ang quiz.

source_string: There was a Realm Event. Check out the Story Feed in Minecraft to see what happened.
translation: Nagkaroon ng Realm Event. Tingnan ang Story Feed sa Minecraft para makita kung ano ang nangyayari.

source_string: There are no available packs on this device.
translation: Walang available na pack sa device na ito.

source_string: Your packs are currently in use.
translation: Ginagamit kasalukuyan ang mga pack mo.

source_string: A pack has errors that will make it not function
translation: May error ang pack na hindi ito papaganahin

source_string: A pack has warnings that might cause odd behavior
translation: May babala ang pack na maaaring magdulot ng kakaibang ugali
(Ilagay dito ang mga file ng resource pack)
Buksan ang folder ng resource pack

source_string: You cannot change Resource Packs while playing in a world.
translation: Hindi mo mababago ang Resource Pack habang naglalaro sa mundo.

source_string: You cannot change Behavior Packs while playing in a world.
translation: Hindi mo mababago ang Behavior Pack habang naglalaro sa mundo.

source_string: This Realm contains resource or behavior packs that have expired from Realms Plus. You will need to either deactivate these packs or purchase them from the marketplace in order to play on the Realm.
translation: May resource pack at behavior pack ang Realm na nag-expire na galing sa Realms Plus. Kailangan mo desaktibahin itong mga pack o bilhin sila sa marketplace para maglaro sa Realm.

source_string: Low memory. Textures will have reduced level of detail.
translation: Mababang memory. Bababa ang pagkadetalyado ng mga texture.

source_string: Resource packs are applied bottom to top. This means any asset that is in two packs will be overridden by the higher pack.
translation: Inilalapat ang Resource pack galing sa baba pataas. Ibig sabihin nito ay papalitan ang anumang asset na nasa dalawang pack ng mas mataas na pack.

source_string: You can edit these in Settings.

Resource packs are applied bottom to top. This means any asset that is in two packs will be overridden by the higher pack. Packs in your worlds will apply on top of these global packs. These resources are just for you. No one else will see the resources you set here. Resource Packs in your worlds or worlds you join will apply on top of these global resources.
translation: Inilalapat ang mga resource pack galing sa baba pataas. Ibig sabihin nito ay papalitan ang anumang asset na nasa dalawang pack ng mas mataas na pack. Ilalapat ang mga pack sa mundo mo sa ibabaw nitong global na pack. Para sa iyo lang ang mga resource na ito. Hindi makikita ninuman ang mga inilagay mong resources dito. Ang mga resource pack na nasa mundo o nasa mundong sinalihan mo ay ilalapat sa ibabaw nitong global na resource.

source_string: Behavior Packs are applied bottom to top. That means anything that is in two Behavior Packs will be overridden by the higher one.
translation: Inilalapat ang Behavior pack galing sa baba pataas. Ibig sabihin nito ay papalitan ang anuman na nasa dalawang Behavior pack ng mas mataas na pack.

source_string: Resource packs are applied bottom to top. This means any asset that is in two packs will be overridden by the higher pack. These packs in your world apply on top of your global pack(s).
translation: Inilalapat ang mga resource pack galing sa baba pataas. Ibig sabihin nito ay papalitan ng anumang asset na nasa dalawang pack ng mas mataas na pack. Ang mga pack sa mundo mo ay ilalapat sa ibabaw ng iyong global na pack.

source_string: Active Behavior Packs apply to all players.
translation: Ilalagay ang aktibong Behavior Pack sa lahat ng manlalaro.

source_string: Require players to download optional resource packs to join
translation: Mangailangang mag-download ang mga manlalaro ng opsiyonal na resource pack para sumali
Nabigong mag-load ang resources noong huli.

source_string: This world may not look or behave in the same way as non-modified worlds. You should save a copy of your world before continuing.
translation: Maaaring hindi gumana at mag-itsura nang parehas sa di-binagong mundo ang mundong ito. Mag-save ka dapat ng kopya ng mundo mo bago magpatuloy.

source_string: There was a problem loading pack %s. Restarting your game or redownloading the pack might solve the issue.
translation: Nagkaproblema sa pag-load ng pack na %s. Maaaring lutasin ang problema ng pag-restart ng iyong laro o pag-download uli ng pack.

source_string: There was a problem loading packs %s. Restarting your game or redownloading the packs might solve the issue.
translation: Nagkaproblema sa pag-load ng mga pack na %s. Maaaring lutasin ang problema ng pag-restart ng iyong laro o pag-download uli ng mga pack.

source_string: Stacking multiple Add-Ons may result in unpredictable experiences. World loading times could vary, and Add-Ons might behave unexpectedly.
translation: Maaaring magdulot ng di-inaasahang karanasan ang pagsasalansan ng maraming Add-On. Maaaring mag-iba ang haba ng oras sa pag-load ng mundo, at maging kakaiba ang ugali ng mga Add-On.

source_string: Removing packs from previously played worlds may result in permanent data loss. We strongly recommend making a copy of your world first!
translation: Maaaring magdulot ng permanenteng pagkawala ng data ang pagtanggal ng pack sa nilarong mundo. Lubos naming iminumungkahi na gumawa ka muna ng kopya ng mundo mo!

source_string: This pack is a required dependency of another pack that is currently applied.
translation: Ang pack na ito ay kinakailangang dependency ng isa pang pack na nakalagay kasalukuyan.

source_string: This pack is missing one or more dependencies. Would you like to apply it anyway?
translation: Nawawalan ang pack na ito ng isa o marami pang dependency. Gusto mo pa ba rin bang ilagay ito?

source_string: You are about to delete %s forever. Are you sure?
translation: Buburahin mo na ang %s nang habang-buhay. Sigurado ka ba?

source_string: This pack is currently selected! You are about to delete %s forever. Are you sure?
translation: Kasalukuyang nakapili itong pack! Buburahin mo na ang %s nang habang-buhay. Sigurado ka ba?

source_string: You are going to delete the following packs forever:%sAre you sure?
translation: Buburahin mo na ang sumusunod na pack nang habang-buhay:%sSigurado ka ba?

source_string: This account does not own this resource pack.
translation: Hindi pag-aari ng account na ito ang resource pack na ito.

source_string: This pack has a dependency (%s) that is incompatible with your device
translation: May dependency ang pack na ito (%s) na incompatible sa device na ito

source_string: This pack has a dependency (%s) that is incompatible with your device because your device doesn't have enough memory.
translation: May dependency ang pack na ito (%s) na incompatible sa device mo dahil kulang ng memory ang device mo.

source_string: This pack has a dependency (%s) that is incompatible with your device because your device doesn't have compatible hardware to support ray tracing
translation: May dependency ang pack na ito (%s) na incompatible sa device mo dahil walang compatible na hardware ang device mo na susuporta sa ray tracing

source_string: This pack is incompatible with your device.
translation: Incompatible itong pack sa iyong device.

source_string: This resolution is incompatible with your device because your device doesn't have enough memory.
translation: Incompatible ang resolusyon na ito sa device mo dahil kulang ng memory ang device mo.

source_string: This pack contains information to allow ray tracing, but your device does not support this option.
translation: May impormasyon itong pack na pumayag mag-ray tracing, pero hindi suportado ng device mo ang opsiyon na ito.

source_string: Looks for worlds from an older version of Minecraft. This might take a while to finish.
translation: Maghahanap ng mundo galing sa lumang version ng Minecraft. Maaaring matagal itong matapos.

source_string: Click a world to convert it into a playable world
translation: Pumindot sa isang mundo para gawin itong nalalarong mundo

source_string: Looks for worlds from the retail version of Minecraft. This might take a while to finish.
translation: Maghahanap ng mundo galing sa retail na version ng Minecraft. Maaaring magtagal ito para matapos.

source_string: Click a world to convert it into a playable preview world
translation: Pumindot sa isang mundo para gawin itong nalalarong preview na mundo

source_string: You have converted your world. You can now find it in “all worlds”.
translation: Kinumberti mo na ang mundo mo. Mahahanap mo na ito sa "lahat ng mundo".

source_string: We have found %s old worlds from a previous version of Minecraft.
translation: Nakahanap kami ng %s lumang mundo galing sa dating version ng Minecrafft.

source_string: We have found %s retail worlds from the Retail version of Minecraft.
translation: Nakahanap kami ng %s retail na mundo galing sa retail na version ng Minecrafft.

source_string: You need to convert "%s" into the latest version of Minecraft to make it playable.
translation: Kailangan mong kumbertihin ang "%s" sa pinakabagong version ng Minecraft para gawin itong nalalaro.
Birch na Bangka na May Baul
Gubat na Bangka na May Baul
Madilim na Robleng Bangka na May Baul

source_string: Tap jump to exit the boat
translation: Pindutin ang talon para umalis sa bangka
Pindutin ang :_input_key.jump: para umalis sa bangka
Pindutin ang :_input_key.jump: para umalis sa balsa

source_string: Tap jump to exit the raft
translation: Pindutin ang talon para umalis sa bansa

source_string: Item can't be upgraded this way
translation: Hindi naa-upgrade ang aytem nang ganito

source_string: Add Diamond armor, weapon, or tool
translation: Maglagay ng armadura, armas, o kagamitang Diyamante
Maglagay ng baretang materyal o kristal

source_string: Want to get the most out of your equipment? You'll need a Smithing Table.
translation: Gusto mo bang sulitin ang kagamitan mo? Kakailanganin mo ng Pandayang Mesa.

source_string: Use it to make all kinds of changes, for example by upgrading Diamond equipment to Netherite, or by making cosmetic changes with Armor Trims.
translation: Gamitin ito para gumawa ng iba-ibang pagbabago, halimbawa pag-upgrade ng Diyamanteng kagamitan sa Netherayt, o paggawa ng kosmetikong pagbabago gamit ang Gayak sa Armadura.

source_string: In order to upgrade your equipment, you'll need a Smithing Template. You can find a large variety throughout the world, which can be used for all kinds of upgrades.
translation: Para i-upgrade ang iyong kagamitan, kakailanganin mo ng Padrong Pampanday. Makakikita ka ng sari-sari nito sa mundo, na magagamit sa paggawa ng iba-ibang upgrade.

source_string: Place a Template into the leftmost slot of a Smithing Table to see which items you need for the upgrade.
translation: Maglagay ng Padron sa pinakakaliwang slot ng Pandayang Mesa para makita ang mga aytem na kailangan mo sa upgrade.

source_string: For example, to upgrade Diamond equipment to Netherite, you need a Netherite Upgrade Smithing Template, which you can find in Bastion Remnants. Then, place the Diamond equipment in the equipment slot and a Netherite ingot in the ingredient slot, and you're done!
translation: Halimbawa, para i-upgrade ang Diyamanteng kagamitan sa Netherayt, kakailanganin mo ng Padrong Pampanday ng Netherayt Upgrade, na mahahanap mo sa Labing Bastion. Pagkatapos, ilagay ang Diyamanteng kagamitan sa slot ng kagamitan at ang Baretang Netherayt sa slot ng kasangkapan, at tapos ka na!

source_string: Item properties such as enchantments and armor trims will be retained, but the Smithing Template will be consumed when you upgrade your equipment. Don't worry - you can craft copies of them with your Crafting Table.
translation: Mananatili ang mga katangian ng aytem tulad ng agimat at gayak, pero uubusin ang Padrong Pampanday ng pag-upgrade ng kagamitan. Huwag mag-alala - makagagawa ka ng kopya nito gamit ang Gawaang Mesa.

source_string: Get creative and customize the look of your armor with Armor Trims. You'll need an Armor Trim Smithing Template to get started, which you can find throughout the world.
translation: Maging malikhain at personalisahin ang itsura ng armadura mo gamit ang Gayak sa Armadura. Kakailanganin mo ng Padrong Pampanday ng Gayak sa Armadura, na mahahanap mo sa mundo.

source_string: Place a Template into the leftmost slot of a Smithing Table to see which items you need for the upgrade. Then place a piece of armor in the equipment slot and a crystal or ingot in the ingredient slot. Done!
translation: Maglagay ng Padron sa pinakakaliwang slot ng Pandayang Mesa para makita kung aling aytem ang kailangan mo para mag-upgrade. Tapos maglagay ng piraso ng armadura sa slot ng kagamitan at ng kristal o baretang materyal sa slot ng kasangkapan. Tapos!

source_string: Only certain crystals and ingots can be used for Armor Trims. Try different kinds like Iron, Gold, or Lapis to create unique designs!
translation: May tiyak lamang na kristal at baretang materyal na magagamit sa Gayak sa Armadura. Sumubok ng iba-ibang uri tulad ng Bakal, Ginto, o Lapis para gumawa ng magandang disenyo!
Madilim na Robleng Nakasabit na Karatula
Sirang Puso na Bibinga ng Palayok

source_string: Are you sure you want to delete the selected items? These items will be lost forever! (A long time!) %s%s%s
translation: Gusto mo ba talagang burahin ang piniling aytem? Mawawala ang aytem na ito nang habang-buhay! (Mahabang panahon!) %s%s%s

source_string: You can redownload content you've bought from the Marketplace.
translation: Mada-download mo uli ang mga content na binili mo sa Marketplace.

source_string: Deleting templates may cause worlds that are using them to no longer work as intended.
translation: Kapag nagbura ka ng template, maaaring hindi na gumana ang mga mundong gumagamit nitong template.

source_string: The following worlds may stop working as intended:
translation: Maaaring hindi na maayos gumana ang susunod na mga mundo:

source_string: This will delete all screenshots for all Minecraft players on this device. Are you sure you want to continue?

source_string: With a Realm subscription, you can create a new %s Realm using the “Create New” button in the main menu. If you don’t have a Realms subscription yet, please go to the full version of Minecraft to sign up.
translation: Sa Realm subscription, makagagawa ka ng bagong %s Realm gamit ang "Gumawa ng Bago" na button sa main menu. Kung wala ka pang Realms subscription, pumunta sa buong version ng Minecraft para mag-sign up.

source_string: All Realms screens and functions are available in %s except purchasing a new subscription or managing the subscriptions of existing Realms.
translation: Available sa %s ang lahat ng screen at function ng Realm maliban sa pagbili ng bagong subscription o pamamahala ng subcription sa nariyan nang Realms.

source_string: Your %s Realm will remain active for as long as you have the paid Realm subscription that your %s Realm is linked to.

source_string: Realms Plus is a subscription to a personal server supporting up to 10 simultaneous players, along with unlimited access to 150+ great Minecraft worlds, texture packs, skin packs, and mash-ups for one low monthly price.
translation: Ang Realms Plus ay isang subscription sa isang personal na server na sumusuporta sa hanggang 10 manlalaro nang sabay-sabay, kasama ng walang-hanggang akses sa 150+ na magagandang mundo sa Minecraft, texture pack, skin pack, at mash-up sa mababang buwanang halaga.

source_string: A personal server allows you to create a shared world that is always online and accessible from any device with Minecraft Marketplace. Players that you invite to your Realm can play this world at any time.
translation: Sa personal na server, makagagawa ka ng sama-samang mundo na laging online at nabubuksan sa anumang device na may Minecraft Marketplace. Ang mga manlalarong inimbita mo sa Realm mo ay makapaglalaro ng mundong ito kailaman.

source_string: Do my friends need to purchase Realms Plus to play on my Realm?
translation: Kailangan ba ng mga kaibigan kong bilhin ang Realms Plus para maglaro sa aking Realm?

source_string: Your friends don’t need to purchase a Realms Plus subscription to play on your Realm. You can invite any friend (that has their multiplayer permissions enabled) to join your Realm for free.
translation: Hindi kailangan ng kaibigan mong bumili ng subscription sa Realms Plus para makapaglaro sa Realm mo. Makapag-iimbita ka ninumang kaibigan (na nakabukas ang kanilang karapatang multiplayer) na sumali sa iyong Realm nang libre.

source_string: Which devices support Realms Plus for Minecraft?
translation: Aling mga device ang sumusuporta ng Realms Plus sa Minecraft?

source_string: Realms Plus is currently available on any platform where you can install Minecraft Bedrock Edition. You can play Realms and use any content from Realms Plus on any of these devices if you’re signed into your Microsoft account.
translation: Kasalukuyang available ang Realms Plus sa anumang platform na napaglalagyan ng Minecraft Bedrock Edition. Makagagamit ka ng Realms at ng anumang content mula sa Realms Plus sa alinmang device na ito kung naka-sign in ka sa iyong Microsoft account.
context: disable_3rd_party_console_resource_pack_check

source_string: How much does a Realms Plus subscription cost?
translation: Magkano ang subscription sa Realms Plus?

source_string: %s per month for a 10-player server and access to 150+ marketplace packs.
translation: %s bawat buwan para sa 10-ang manlalaro na server at akses sa 150+ na marketplace pack.

source_string: %s per month. Add infinite members, play online with 10 other players at the same time. Plus, enjoy over 150 pieces of Marketplace content from the Marketplace Pass catalog for free.

source_string: How often are new packs added to Realms Plus?

translation: Buwan-buwan nagkakaroon ng bagong pack sa Realms Plus.

source_string: How long do I have access to Packs within Realms Plus?

source_string: Realms Plus members enjoy unlimited access to over 150+ great Minecraft worlds, texture packs, skin packs, and mash-ups, until either the subscription expires, or a pack leaves the catalog.
translation: Makagagamit ang miyembro ng Realms Plus ng aabot sa 150+ na magagandang mundo sa Minecraft, texture pack, skin pack, at mash-up hanggang mag-expire ang subscription, o mawala ang pack sa catalog.

source_string: Where can I use Realms Plus packs?
translation: Saan ko magagamit ang pack ng Realms Plus?

source_string: Worlds and packs included in the subscription can either be played online, played on your personal Realm, or played on a local device. You just need to play online once every 30 days to validate that your subscription is active.
translation: Ang mga mundo at pack na kasama sa subscription ay malalaro online, sa iyong personal na Realm, o sa lokal na device. Kailangan mo lang maglaro online bawat 30 araw para kumpirmahing aktibo pa rin ang iyong subscription.

source_string: What happens to my Realms and worlds when my subscription expires?
translation: Ano ang mangyayari sa aking Realms at mundo kapag lumipas ang subscription ko?

source_string: If your subscription ends, you and your friends will no longer be able to play online together on Realms, and you will no longer have access to Realms Plus packs. You can download any world saved to your Realm (within 18 months of ending your subscription). If you used Realms Plus worlds, texture packs, or mash-ups you will need to purchase those packs in the store or, if those packs are still in Realms Plus, re-subscribe, to play those world templates.
translation: Kung lumipas ang subscription mo, hindi na makapaglalaro ikaw at mga kaibigan mo online nang magkakasama sa Realms, at hindi ka na magkakaakses sa mga pack sa Realms Plus. Mada-download mo ang anumang mundo na naka-save sa iyong Realm (sa loob ng 18 buwan ng pagtapos ng subscription mo). Kung gumamit ka ng mundo, texture pack, o mash-up ng Realms Plus, kakailanganin mong bilhin ang mga pack na iyon sa store o, kung nasa Realms Plus pa rin ang mga pack na iyon, mag-subscribe uli para laruin ang mga template ng mundong iyon.

Download and play adventure maps, wear skins, dive into texture packs, and even claim a set of Character Creator items to keep each month. source_string: Marketplace Pass is a subscription for content to be used with supported versions of Minecraft (game sold separately) on Windows and other supported platforms on which you own the game (Minecraft Java & Amazon Kindle Fire Editions not supported); an active subscription is required to use Marketplace Pass content. Content varies over time and may not be available in all countries. After the free trial period, subscription continues to be charged at the then-current regular price (subject to change) plus applicable taxes unless cancelled. You can cancel your subscription by accessing Services & subscriptions in your Microsoft account. If your subscription terminates or a content item is removed from the catalog, you must reactivate your subscription or buy the content separately to continue using it. ISP fees may apply. We may occasionally provide content that remains available to you even after the end of your subscription, in which case we reserve the right to take down such content if it becomes incompatible or if our rights to the content expire. Subscription subject to change and/or retirement. Subject to the Microsoft Services Agreement (www.microsoft.com/msa) and the Minecraft EULA (https://www.minecraft.net/eula). Any translations of these terms are done for your convenience only, and in the event of a dispute between the English and any non-English versions, the English version of these terms shall govern.
translation: Ang Marketplace Pass ay isang subscription sa content para gamitin sa suportadong version ng Minecraft (hiwalay ipinagbibili ang laro) sa Windows at iba pang suportadong platform kung saan pagmamay-ari mo ang laro (hindi suportado ang Minecraft Java & Amazon Kindle Fire Edition); kailangan ng aktibong subscription para gumamit ng content sa Marketplace Pass. Nagbabago sa oras ang content at maaaring hindi available sa lahat ng bansa. Pagkatapos ng panahon ng libreng trial, tuloy na sisingilin ang subscription sa halaga ng dati (sumasailalim sa pagbabago) kasama ng kaukulang buwis maliban kung kinansela. Makakansela mo ang subscription mo gamit ang Services & subscription sa iyong Microsoft account. Kung nagtapos ang subscription mo o tinanggal ang content sa catalog, kailangang mong ireaktiba ang subscription mo o bilhin nang hiwalay ang content para tuloy na gamitin. Maaaring umiral ang ISP fee. Maaari kaming minsan magbigay ng content na mananatiling available para sa iyo matapos man ang subscription mo, kung saan may karapatan kaming tanggalin ang naturang content kung hindi na ito compatible o lumipas na ang karapatan namin sa content. Sumasailalim sa pagbabago at pagreretira ang subscription. Napapasailalim ito sa Microsoft Services Agreement (www.microsoft.com/msa) at Minecraft EULA (https://www.minecraft.net/eula). Ang anumang salin sa terminong ito ay para sa pagpapadali lamang, at sa pagkakataon ng di-pagkakasundo ng bersiyong Ingles at bersiyong di-ingles, iigting ang bersiyong Ingles ng terminong ito.

I-unlock ang Buong Version ng Minecraft

source_string: Endlessly explore your own unique worlds and construct anything you can imagine - from the simplest of homes to the grandest of castles! Play Creative mode to build wonders with unlimited resources. Or mine in Survival mode, crafting weapons and armor to fend off dangerous mobs and survive the nights. Plus, play with friends online! Unlock the full game today!
translation: Walang-tigil na lakbayin ang sarili mong mundo at gumawa ng kahit anong maisip mo - galing sa pinakasimple na bahay hanggang sa pinakagrandeng kastilyo! Maglaro ng Creative mode para magtayo ng kahanga-hangang gusali gamit ang walang-hanggang aytem. O magmina sa Survival mode, gumawa ng armas at armadura para magsangga ng mapanganip na mob at mabuhay sa gabi. At saka maglaro online kasama ang kaibigan! I-unlock na ang buong laro ngayon!

source_string: With the full Minecraft experience you get Creative mode, achievements, and more, plus with a Microsoft account you can meet others in the Minecraft community! Join your friends' worlds, make new friends on Servers, and sync your Marketplace purchases to everywhere you play Minecraft.
translation: Sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft, makakukuha ka ng Creative mode, tagumpay, at iba pa, at saka sa Microsoft account, makahahalubilo ka ng iba sa komunidad ng Minecraft! Salihan ang mundo ng kaibigan mo, gumawa ng bagong kaibigan sa mga Server, at i-sync ang iyong binili sa Marketplace saan ka man naglalaro ng Minecraft.

source_string: In addition to the full Minecraft experience with Creative mode, Multiplayer, and more, you'll earn achievements and a Gamerscore to mark your Minecraft progress and show your Microsoft account friends your accomplishments. Get the full game to start earning them!
translation: Kasama ng Creative mode, Multiplayer, at iba pa ng buong karanasan ng Minecraft, makakukuha ka ng tagumpay at Gamerscore para markahin ang progreso mo sa Minecraft at ipakita sa mga kaibigan mo sa Microsoft account ang mga nakamit mo. Kunin ang buong laro ngayon para simulan itong kamitin!

source_string: The full Minecraft experience lets you enjoy Creative mode, achievements and Multiplayer with your friends across Minecraft devices! Play with friends on console, PC and mobile to create, explore and survive together. Unlock the full Minecraft experience today!
translation: Sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft, magkakaroon ka ng Creative mode, tagumpay, at Multiplayer kasama ang kaibigan sa iba-ibang device! Maglaro kasama ang kaibigang nasa console, PC at mobile para gumawa, maglakbay, at mabuhay sama-sama. I-unlock na ang buong karanasan ng Minecraft ngayon!

source_string: Servers offer some of the most creative ways to enjoy Minecraft! Play great mini-games, meet the Minecraft community and make new friends. Unlock the full Minecraft experience to try Servers today!
translation: Nagbibigay ang mga Server ng mga malikhaing paraan para maglaro ng Minecraft! Maglaro ng magagaling na mini-game, makipaghalubilo sa komunidad ng Minecraft at gumawa ng bagong kaibigan. I-unlock na ang buong karanasan ng Minecraft ngayon para subukan ang mga Server!

source_string: Get access to Minecraft Marketplace, our in-game store. Switch up your look with new skins, change your world, or explore incredible new maps from the best community creators! Get the full game today!
translation: Magkaakses sa Minecraft Marketplace, ang aming store sa loob ng laro. Palitan ang dating mo gamit ang bagong skin, baguhin ang mundo mo, at tahakin ang kahanga-hanga at bagong mundo galing sa aming pinakamagagaling na creator sa komunidad! Kunin na ang buong laro ngayon!

source_string: Buy Minecraft and get Creative mode! Access the entire inventory - the only limit to what you can build is your imagination! Fly around your world, make your dream home out of anything and everything, or just blow up a mountain with unlimited TNT!
translation: Bilhin ang Minecraft at magkaroon ng Creative mode! Aksesin ang buong imbentaryo - ang hangganan lang ng kaya mong tayuin ay ang imahinasyon mo! Lumipad-lipad sa mundo mo, gawin ang pangarap mong bahay gamit ang anuman, o magpasabog ng bundok gamit ang walang-hanggang TNT!

source_string: Want to make wolves act like bunnies? Turn all the trees into cotton candy? You can alter everything in the full Minecraft experience with add-ons! Plus get access to Multiplayer, Creative mode, achievements and more! Buy Minecraft now for full access!
translation: Gusto mo bang magmalakuneho ang mga lobo? Gawing cotton candy ang lahat ng puno? Mababago mo ang lahat sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft gamit ang mga add-on! At saka magkaakses sa Multiplayer, Creative mode, tagumpay at iba pa! Bilhin ang Minecraft ngayon para sa buong akses!

source_string: Unlock the full Minecraft experience and get access to Seeds! Seeds help you discover new biomes - survive on ice plains, ascend extreme hills, or trek across deserts. Start with unique templates or explore random new worlds! Access Seeds, Creative mode, Multiplayer and more by buying Minecraft today!
translation: I-unlock ang buong karanasan ng Minecraft at magkaakses sa Seed! Tutulungan ka ng Seed na makatuklas ng bagong mga biome - mabuhay sa parang ng yelo, umakyat sa matatarik na burol, o tahakin ang disyerto. Magsimula sa mga padron o maglakbay sa mga random na bagong mundo! Magkaakses sa Seed, Multiplayer, at iba pa sa pagbili ngayon ng Minecraft!

source_string: Thank you for downloading the Minecraft Trial for Chromebook! Your playtesting will provide invaluable data for bug fixes and technical troubleshooting. Uncover a bug? Report it at bugs.mojang.com! Other questions? Check out our FAQ.
translation: Salamat sa pag-download ng Minecraft Trial sa Chromebook! Magbibigay ng mahalagang datos ang playtesting mo para sa pag-ayos ng bug at teknikal na troubleshooting. Nakakita ng bug? Iulat ito sa bugs.mojang.com! May ibang tanong? Tingnan ang aming FAQ.

source_string: With the full Minecraft experience, you get Creative mode, achievements, and more, plus with a Microsoft account you can meet others in the Minecraft community! You’ll be able to join friends’ worlds, make new friends on Servers, and sync your Marketplace purchases to everywhere you play Minecraft.
translation: Sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft, makakukuha ka ng Creative mode, tagumpay, at iba pa, at saka sa Microsoft account, makahahalubilo ka ng iba sa komunidad ng Minecraft! Masasalihan mo ang mundo ng kaibigan mo, makagagawa ng bagong kaibigan sa mga Server, at makapagsi-sync ng iyong binili sa Marketplace saan ka man naglalaro ng Minecraft.

source_string: In addition to the full Minecraft experience with Creative mode, Multiplayer, and more, you'll earn achievements and a Gamerscore to mark your Minecraft progress and show your Microsoft account friends your accomplishments.
translation: Kasama ng Creative mode, Multiplayer, at iba pa ng buong karanasan ng Minecraft, makakukuha ka ng tagumpay at Gamerscore para markahin ang progreso mo sa Minecraft at ipakita sa mga kaibigan mo sa Microsoft account ang mga nakamit mo.

source_string: The full Minecraft experience lets you enjoy Creative mode, achievements and Multiplayer with your friends across Minecraft devices! Play with friends on console, PC and mobile to create, explore and survive together.
translation: Sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft, magkakaroon ka ng Creative mode, tagumpay, at Multiplayer kasama ang kaibigan sa iba-ibang device! Maglaro kasama ang kaibigang nasa console, PC at mobile para gumawa, maglakbay, at mabuhay sama-sama.

source_string: As a part of the full Minecraft experience, Servers offer some of the most creative ways to enjoy Minecraft! Play great mini-games, meet the Minecraft community and make new friends.
translation: Bilang parte ng buong karanasan ng Minecraft, magbibigay ang mga Server ng ilan sa mga pinakamalikhaing paraan sa paglaro ng Minecraft! Maglaro ng magagaling na mini-game, makihalubilo sa komunidad ng Minecraft at gumawa ng bagong kaibigan.

source_string: The full game allows access to Minecraft Marketplace, our in-game store. Switch up your look with new skins, change your world, or explore incredible new maps from the best community creators!
translation: Sa buong laro, magkaakses ka sa Minecraft Marketplace, ang aming store sa loob ng laro. Palitan ang dating mo gamit ang bagong skin, baguhin ang mundo mo, at tahakin ang kahanga-hanga at bagong mundo galing sa aming pinakamagagaling na creator sa komunidad!

source_string: A beloved part of the full Minecraft experience: Creative mode! Access the entire inventory - the only limit to what you can build is your imagination! Fly around your world, make your dream home out of anything and everything, or just blow up a mountain with unlimited TNT!
translation: Ang tinatanging parte ng buong karanasan ng Minecraft: ang Creative mode! Aksesin ang buong imbentaryo - ang hangganan lang ng kaya mong tayuin ay ang imahinasyon mo! Lumipad-lipad sa mundo mo, gawin ang pangarap mong bahay gamit ang anuman, o magpasabog ng bundok gamit ang walang-hanggang TNT!

source_string: Want to make wolves act like bunnies? Turn all the trees into cotton candy? You can alter everything in the full Minecraft experience with add-ons! Plus get access to Multiplayer, Creative mode, achievements and more!
translation: Gusto mo bang magmalakuneho ang mga lobo? Gawing cotton candy ang lahat ng puno? Mababago mo ang lahat sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft gamit ang mga add-on! At saka magkaakses sa Multiplayer, Creative mode, tagumpay at iba pa!

source_string: The full Minecraft experience unlocks access to Seeds! Seeds help you discover new biomes - survive on ice plains, ascend extreme hills, or trek across deserts. Start with unique templates or explore random new worlds!
translation: Sa buong karanasan ng Minecraft, magkaakses ka sa Seed! Tutulungan ka ng Seed na makatuklas ng bagong mga biome - mabuhay sa parang ng yelo, umakyat sa matatarik na burol, o tahakin ang disyerto. Magsimula sa mga padron o maglakbay sa mga random na bagong mundo!

source_string: Get Minecraft, 700 Minecoins, 2 skin packs, 1 texture pack and 1 mash-up
translation: Magkaroon ng Minecraft, 700 Minecoin, 2 skin pack, 1 texture pack at 1 mash-up

source_string: Get Minecraft, 1000 Minecoins, 4 skin packs, 2 texture packs, 3 maps, and 1 mash-up
translation: Magkaroon ng Minecraft, 2000 Minecoin, 4 skin pack, 2 texture pack, 3 mapa, at 1 mash-up

source_string: Buy skins, textures and worlds in the Marketplace!
translation: Bumili ng skin, texture, at mundo sa Marketplace!

source_string: Buy skins, textures and worlds in the Marketplace!
translation: Bumili ng skin, texture, at mundo sa Marketplace!

source_string: Go on safari in a rugged off-road vehicle that seats 4!
translation: Mag-safari sa matatag na off-road vehicle na nag-uupo ng 4!

source_string: Explore Noxcrew's magical world full of ancient castles!
translation: Lakbayin ang mahiwagang mundo ni Noxcrew na puno ng sinaunang kastilyo!

source_string: Transform your Minecraft world into a comic!
translation: Transpormahin ang mundo mo sa Minecraft sa komiks!

source_string: Vast tropical wilderness on a whirlwind hunt for treasure!
translation: Mabuhawing paghahanap ng kayamanan sa malawak na tropikal na ilang!

source_string: Explore an ancient world, texture pack and skins!
translation: Maglakbay sa sinaunang mundo, may texture pack at skin!

source_string: Playgrounds filled with games and challenges!
translation: Larang na puno ng laro at pagsubok!

source_string: Get ready for an explosion of rainbow pastel happiness!
Make your worlds simple, colorful and vibrant!
translation: Gawing simple, makulay at masigla ang mundo mo!

source_string: Customize your character with this selection of skins!
translation: Personalisahin ang karakter mo sa seleksiyong ito ng skin!

source_string: Dress as a Cake Maniac, Frankencrafter, or Worse!
translation: Magbihis bilang Cake Maniac, Frankencrafter, o mas masama!

source_string: The original Minecraft experience: collect resources to craft tools and build structures, find and farm food to manage your hunger, battle dangerous mobs, and explore a vast world.
translation: Ang orihinal na karanasan ng Minecraft: mangalap ng materyales para gumawa ng kagamitan at magtayo ng estruktura, maghanap at magsaka ng pagkain para asikasuhin ang gutom mo, makipaglaban sa mga mapapanganib na mob, at maglakbay sa malawak na mundo.

source_string: Start by collecting some wood and dirt for a makeshift home to help you survive the first night! From there it's all up to you.
translation: Magsimula sa pagkolekta ng kahoy at lupa para sa isang gawa-gawang bahay para tulungan kang mabuhay sa unang gabi! Pagkatapos noon, ikaw na lang mag-isa.

source_string: Build anything you can imagine in Creative Mode. Take no damage, fly through the skies, and enjoy instant access to every block in the game! This mode lets you focus on crafting and gives you everything you need to build something beautiful!
translation: Gumawa ng anumang naiisip sa Creative Mode. Walang damage, lumipad sa langit, at magkaakses sa lahat ng bloke sa laro! Sa mode na ito, mapagtutuunan mo ang paggawa at bibigay sa iyo ng anumang kailangan mo para magtayo ng magandang bagay!

source_string: You'll also have access to Inspiration Island, a tutorial world and introduction to Creative mode that'll teach you how to be a master builder in no time! You can find more great worlds like this in Minecraft Marketplace.
translation: Magkakaakses ka rin sa Isla ng Inspirasyon, isang tutorial na mundo na introduksiyon sa Creative mode na magtuturo sa iyo kung paano maging dalubhasang builder! Makahahanap ka pa ng magagaling na mundong tulad nito sa Minecraft Marketplace.

source_string: We're having trouble verifying that you own Minecraft on this device. Make sure you have downloaded and installed Minecraft from the store. Or simply reconnect to the internet and try again.
translation: Nagkakaproblema kami sa pagberipika na pagmamay-ari mo ang Minecraft sa device na ito. Siguraduhing i-dinownload mo at ininstall ang Minecraft sa store. O magrekonekta lang sa internet at subukang muli.

source_string: When you see this icon, we are saving your game. Do not turn off your device while this icon is on screen.
translation: Kapag nakita mo ang icon na ito, isine-save namin ang laro mo. Huwag patayin ang device mo habang nakalabas sa screen itong icon.

source_string: When you see this icon, we are saving your game. Do not turn off your Xbox while this icon is on screen.
translation: Kapag nakita mo ang icon na ito, isine-save namin ang laro mo. Huwag patayin ang Xbox mo habang nakalabas sa screen itong icon.

source_string: When you see this icon, we are saving your game. Do not turn off your computer while this icon is on screen.

source_string: Please sign in with your Microsoft account to play with friends, earn gamerscore and achievements.
translation: Mag-sign in gamit ang iyong Microsoft account para maglaro kasama ang kaibigan, magkamit ng gamerscore at tagumpay.

source_string: Thanks for testing Realms! The features are not final and you might run into bugs. Send us feedback! We're listening.
translation: Salamat sa pag-test ng Realms! Hindi pinal ang mga feature na ito at may maaari kang madatnang bug. Padalhan kami ng feedback! Nakikinig kami.

source_string: During this test, everyone will need to sign in with a Microsoft account so they can be sent invites and added to Realms.
translation: Sa test na ito, kailangan ng lahat na mag-sign in gamit ng Microsoft account para mapadalhan sila ng imbita at malagay sa Realms.

source_string: This will send you back to the main menu. Continue?

source_string: Your current skin violates our Community Standards. Please select a different skin to join a multiplayer game. Click "%s" to view our Community Standards or submit a case review for your current skin.

source_string: This is bad. This server failed our verification test. Someone we don't trust might be pretending to be a trusted server.
